WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.870
You will remain secure and rest in the

00:00:01.880 --> 00:00:04.670
shadow of the Almighty, whose power no

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:07.270
enemy can withstand.

00:00:07.280 --> 00:00:09.710
I will say of the Lord,

00:00:09.720 --> 00:00:13.750
'He is my refuge and my fortress, my God

00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:16.830
in whom I trust with great confidence

00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:19.030
and on whom I

00:00:19.030 --> 00:00:19.040
rely.'For

00:00:19.040 --> 00:00:21.310
he will save you

00:00:21.320 --> 00:00:23.430
from the trap of the fowler

00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:25.910
and from the deadly pestilence.

00:00:25.920 --> 00:00:28.750
He will cover you and completely

00:00:28.760 --> 00:00:31.710
protect you with his pinions, and under

00:00:31.720 --> 00:00:34.830
his wings you will find refuge.

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:38.830
His faithfulness is a shield and a wall.

00:00:38.840 --> 00:00:40.870
You will not be afraid of the terror of

00:00:40.880 --> 00:00:43.870
the night, nor the arrow that flies by

00:00:43.880 --> 00:00:46.830
day, nor the pestilence that stalks

00:00:46.840 --> 00:00:49.830
in darkness, nor the destruction and

00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:53.110
sudden death that lays waste at noon.

00:00:53.120 --> 00:00:55.550
A thousand may fall at your side and

00:00:55.560 --> 00:00:58.110
10,000 at your right hand, but

00:00:58.110 --> 00:00:58.120
no

00:00:58.120 --> 00:01:01.150
danger will come near you.

00:01:01.160 --> 00:01:04.110
You will only be a spectator as you look

00:01:04.120 --> 00:01:06.150
on with your eyes and witness the divine

00:01:06.160 --> 00:01:08.310
repayment of the wicked as you watch

00:01:08.320 --> 00:01:11.350
safely

00:01:11.360 --> 00:01:13.590
from the shelter of the Most High.

00:01:13.600 --> 00:01:16.030
Because you have made the Lord, who is

00:01:16.040 --> 00:01:18.230
my refuge, even the Most High, your

00:01:18.240 --> 00:01:21.510
dwelling place, no evil will befall you,

00:01:21.520 --> 00:01:24.310
nor will any plague come near your tent.

00:01:24.320 --> 00:01:26.270
For he will command his angels in

00:01:26.280 --> 00:01:29.230
regards to you to protect and defend and

00:01:29.240 --> 00:01:32.150
guard you in all your ways of obedience

00:01:32.160 --> 00:01:34.310
and service. They will lift you up in

00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:37.030
their hands so that you do not even

00:01:37.040 --> 00:01:39.630
strike your foot against a stone. You

00:01:39.640 --> 00:01:41.830
will tread upon the lion and the cobra,

00:01:41.840 --> 00:01:43.670
the young lion and the serpent. You will

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:45.230
trample

00:01:45.230 --> 00:01:45.240
underfoot

00:01:45.240 --> 00:01:48.230
because he has set his love on me.

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:51.310
Therefore, I will save him. I will set

00:01:51.320 --> 00:01:53.990
him securely on high because he knows my

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:56.990
name. He confidently trusts and relies

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:00.030
on me, knowing I will never abandon him.

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:01.990
No, never.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:04.110
He will call upon me and I will answer

00:02:04.120 --> 00:02:06.830
him. I will be with him in trouble. I

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:09.669
will rescue him and honor him

00:02:11.080 --> 00:02:14.150
with long life.

00:02:20.040 --> 00:02:23.150
I will satisfy him and I will let him

00:02:23.160 --> 00:02:27.230
see my salvation. Amen.

00:02:27.240 --> 00:02:29.750
I love that. With long

00:02:29.750 --> 00:02:29.760
life—long

00:02:29.760 --> 00:02:32.390
abundant life

00:02:32.390 --> 00:02:32.400
and

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:34.750
abundance to the full until it

00:02:34.760 --> 00:02:36.270
overflows.

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:38.910
Overflow life, not just barely getting

00:02:38.920 --> 00:02:42.470
by life, but overflow life and abundant

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:46.310
life. How many

00:02:46.310 --> 00:02:46.320
are

00:02:46.320 --> 00:02:47.790
here?

00:02:47.800 --> 00:02:51.070
Well, good morning, family. Praise the

00:02:51.080 --> 00:02:53.030
Lord. It's evening time, but I like

00:02:53.040 --> 00:02:54.876
