00:11:01.240 --> 00:11:04.150
touched on that enough. So, let's

00:11:04.160 --> 00:11:06.230
go over

00:11:06.240 --> 00:11:09.510
what happened in the news

00:11:09.520 --> 00:11:13.430
with the FBI. The FBI

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:17.550
caught a group of people in Michigan.

00:11:17.560 --> 00:11:21.030
Where was the main place I saw them

00:11:21.040 --> 00:11:24.390
crossing over from Canada?

00:11:24.400 --> 00:11:25.829
Michigan.

00:11:25.839 --> 00:11:28.670
I told Diana and Braden,

00:11:28.680 --> 00:11:30.750
'That's not a coincidence.'I can even

00:11:30.760 --> 00:11:32.070
tell you where they

00:11:32.080 --> 00:11:33.270
