00:11:33.280 --> 00:11:35.230
I knew exactly where they entered and where

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:37.710
the hub was; I

00:11:37.720 --> 00:11:40.270
saw all of it.

00:11:40.280 --> 00:11:41.990
Some of these men were coming over from

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:44.470
Canada.

00:11:44.470 --> 00:11:44.480
I've

00:11:44.480 --> 00:11:47.110
probably said too much, but

00:11:47.120 --> 00:11:50.070
I've seen some of this. I

00:11:50.070 --> 00:11:50.080
have

00:11:50.080 --> 00:11:51.550
to move on.

00:11:51.560 --> 00:11:53.910
I want you to

00:11:53.920 --> 00:11:55.950
hear that; I'm not going to say anything else.

00:11:59.000 --> 00:12:01.550
Praise the Lord, family. That's what I'm

00:12:01.560 --> 00:12:03.910
talking about right there.

00:12:03.920 --> 00:12:06.670
When the body of

00:12:06.680 --> 00:12:08.990
Christ steps in, look what we do. Isn't

00:12:09.000 --> 00:12:11.390
that exciting? There's much more work to

00:12:11.400 --> 00:12:12.829
be done.

00:12:12.839 --> 00:12:15.430
I was excited about

00:12:15.440 --> 00:12:17.470
that report. I didn't come on yesterday

00:12:17.470 --> 00:12:17.480
to

00:12:17.480 --> 00:12:19.150
tell you that.

00:12:19.160 --> 00:12:22.630
Here is another

00:12:22.640 --> 00:12:26.630
thing that we prayed over. This is

00:12:27.230 --> 00:12:27.240
Marjorie

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:30.190
Taylor Greene.

00:12:32.360 --> 00:12:34.630
Braden found this on Alex; he can't

00:12:34.640 --> 00:12:37.110
play the whole clip, but he can play

00:12:37.120 --> 00:12:38.710
this little part right here. I want you

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:40.430
to play this and see what we prayed

00:12:40.440 --> 00:12:42.430
over

00:12:42.440 --> 00:12:44.070
and what we hear in the news.

00:12:45.630 --> 00:12:45.640
Republicans

00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:51.350
and Democrats can't work

00:12:51.360 --> 00:12:53.110
together, don't work together, and

00:12:53.120 --> 00:12:55.350
refuse to work together.

00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:56.990
That is a fact of where we are in

00:12:57.000 --> 00:12:59.710
America. Why would they sit there and

00:12:59.720 --> 00:13:01.470
banter back and forth and try to get

00:13:01.480 --> 00:13:04.030
seven Democrat votes? You pray over

00:13:04.040 --> 00:13:05.670
those right there. He said, 'Do you see

00:13:05.680 --> 00:13:07.190
that group right there? I see them. It's

00:13:07.190 --> 00:13:07.200
a huddle,

00:13:07.200 --> 00:13:08.510
just a

00:13:08.510 --> 00:13:08.520
few.'I'm

00:13:08.520 --> 00:13:11.470
counting their

00:13:11.470 --> 00:13:11.480
faces:

00:13:11.480 --> 00:13:12.470
one,

00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:13.470
two,

00:13:13.480 --> 00:13:16.790
three, four,

00:13:16.800 --> 00:13:17.870
five,

00:13:17.880 --> 00:13:19.310
six,

00:13:19.320 --> 00:13:21.030
seven.

00:13:21.040 --> 00:13:24.110
Seven.

00:13:24.120 --> 00:13:26.750
And then there's one predominant one.

00:13:32.839 --> 00:13:37.070
'Pray over these few

00:13:37.070 --> 00:13:37.080
here.'She

00:13:37.080 --> 00:13:39.670
said seven Republicans and

00:13:39.680 --> 00:13:41.750
Democrats can't work together and

00:13:41.750 --> 00:13:41.760
refuse to

00:13:41.760 --> 00:13:43.350
work together.

00:13:45.960 --> 00:13:48.270
Why would

00:13:48.280 --> 00:13:50.270
they

00:13:50.280 --> 00:13:52.990
try to get seven Democrat votes?

00:13:54.400 --> 00:13:56.829
I don't know this

00:13:56.839 --> 00:13:58.790
stuff, y'all. I'm not a highly educated

00:13:58.800 --> 00:14:00.550
man, but I follow the Holy

00:14:00.550 --> 00:14:00.560
Spirit.

00:14:00.560 --> 00:14:02.750
It was cool because when I'm

00:14:02.760 --> 00:14:06.190
seeing in the spirit, I see seven faces.

00:14:06.200 --> 00:14:08.390
The Lord said,

00:14:08.400 --> 00:14:09.990
'Count them.'I count the men's

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:12.590
and women's faces. He said, 'All you

00:14:12.600 --> 00:14:15.190
need is to flip those faces. You don't

00:14:15.200 --> 00:14:18.430
need all of them; you just need

00:14:18.430 --> 00:14:18.440
seven.'Then

00:14:18.440 --> 00:14:20.310
I saw one main

00:14:20.320 --> 00:14:21.590
face.

00:14:21.590 --> 00:14:21.600
He

00:14:21.600 --> 00:14:23.430
said, 'This is where we're at tonight.

00:14:23.440 --> 00:14:24.470
We're going to

00:14:24.480 --> 00:14:26.190
pray

00:14:26.200 --> 00:14:29.870
for seven faces

00:14:29.880 --> 00:14:33.310
to soften their hearts toward the budget

00:14:33.320 --> 00:14:36.510
and to open our government for the

00:14:36.510 --> 00:14:36.520
TSA

00:14:36.520 --> 00:14:37.510
and

00:14:37.520 --> 00:14:39.710
for our Homeland

00:14:39.710 --> 00:14:39.720
Security—whoever

00:14:39.720 --> 00:14:42.390
gets paid by this

00:14:42.390 --> 00:14:42.400
budget.'We're

00:14:42.400 --> 00:14:43.870
believing God for your paychecks

00:14:43.880 --> 00:14:45.390
tonight.

00:14:45.400 --> 00:14:47.910
We're believing God for America

00:14:47.920 --> 00:14:50.990
to open up again, for this nonsense

00:14:51.000 --> 00:14:54.150
to stop. I haven't

00:14:54.160 --> 00:14:56.030
seen any rioting today because of the

00:14:56.040 --> 00:14:58.030
SNAP program.

00:15:01.040 --> 00:15:02.470
Look,

00:15:06.839 --> 00:15:08.710
President Trump came on and said

00:15:08.720 --> 00:15:10.590
this: he was trying to figure out

00:15:10.600 --> 00:15:12.270
a way around the budget to

00:15:12.280 --> 00:15:14.510
fund

00:15:14.520 --> 00:15:16.110
food stamps so the people

00:15:16.120 --> 00:15:17.829
didn't go without food.

00:15:17.839 --> 00:15:20.110
'SNAP benefits could expire today for

00:15:20.120 --> 00:15:22.829
more than a million veterans.

00:15:22.839 --> 00:15:24.630
A federal judge ordered emergency funds

00:15:24.640 --> 00:15:26.390
to pay for SNAP yesterday, with President

00:15:26.400 --> 00:15:28.510
Trump saying, "I do not want

00:15:28.520 --> 00:15:30.310
Americans to go hungry just because the

00:15:30.320 --> 00:15:32.270
radical Democrats refuse to do the right

00:15:32.280 --> 00:15:34.350
thing and reopen the government.

00:15:34.360 --> 00:15:36.470
Therefore, I have instructed our lawyers

00:15:36.480 --> 00:15:38.829
to ask the court to clarify how we can

00:15:38.839 --> 00:15:42.510
legally fund SNAP as soon as

00:15:42.520 --> 00:15:43.710
possible."'Thank

00:15:43.720 --> 00:15:45.590
God for that.

00:15:47.600 --> 00:15:49.710
Braden keeps me up to date,

00:15:49.720 --> 00:15:52.750
and I thought, 'Thank

00:15:52.750 --> 00:15:52.760
God.'After

00:15:52.760 --> 00:15:54.230
Braden showed that to me, I said,

00:15:54.240 --> 00:15:56.110
'Well, thank God. Hopefully, he's going to

00:15:56.120 --> 00:15:57.590
get that done so these people

00:15:57.600 --> 00:15:58.670
don't go without.'Braden

00:15:58.670 --> 00:15:58.680
is

00:15:58.680 --> 00:16:01.670
awesome; he's a good kid.

00:16:01.680 --> 00:16:03.510
I appreciate you, Braden.

00:16:03.520 --> 00:16:06.110
Then the other part was Braden

00:16:06.110 --> 00:16:06.120
showing

00:16:06.120 --> 00:16:09.990
me

00:16:09.990 --> 00:16:10.000
that

00:16:10.000 --> 00:16:13.510
Trump threatens Nigeria with potential

00:16:13.520 --> 00:16:18.430
military action. He escalates

00:16:18.440 --> 00:16:20.710
the

00:16:20.720 --> 00:16:22.470
claim of Christian persecution.

00:16:29.440 --> 00:16:33.630
We see him hoping to step in

00:16:33.640 --> 00:16:35.910
and stop the genocide of the

00:16:35.920 --> 00:16:38.790
Christian people in Nigeria.

00:16:38.800 --> 00:16:40.829
We give God all praise for that. We

00:16:40.839 --> 00:16:42.670
want that to stop; it's

00:16:42.680 --> 00:16:45.190
ridiculous. They said 75,000 plus have

00:16:45.200 --> 00:16:46.990
been slaughtered,

00:16:47.000 --> 00:16:49.630
and that is ridiculous.

00:16:49.640 --> 00:16:51.829
Even

00:16:51.839 --> 00:16:53.470
people that we knew

00:16:53.470 --> 00:16:53.480
are

00:16:53.480 --> 00:16:55.110
asking,

00:16:55.120 --> 00:16:56.750
'Please pray for

00:16:56.760 --> 00:16:58.990
us, Brandon.'So we're going to pray

00:16:59.000 --> 00:17:01.110
for them tonight.

00:17:01.120 --> 00:17:02.910
One last thing Braden showed me

00:17:02.920 --> 00:17:05.150
today was a

00:17:05.150 --> 00:17:05.160
report

00:17:05.160 --> 00:17:07.590
that

00:17:07.590 --> 00:17:07.600
the

00:17:07.600 --> 00:17:10.069
Pentagon cleared giving Ukraine

00:17:10.079 --> 00:17:13.750
long-range Tomahawk missiles, leaving

00:17:13.750 --> 00:17:13.760
the

00:17:13.760 --> 00:17:17.230
final decision to Trump.

00:17:17.240 --> 00:17:19.669
The Pentagon is saying today

00:17:19.679 --> 00:17:22.110
they want to give those Tomahawk

00:17:22.120 --> 00:17:24.189
missiles that I saw in the spirit back

00:17:24.189 --> 00:17:24.199
when

00:17:24.199 --> 00:17:26.230
I was in Branson. I was

00:17:26.240 --> 00:17:28.030
praying and the Lord showed me those

00:17:28.040 --> 00:17:32.590
Tomahawk missiles going into Moscow,

00:17:32.600 --> 00:17:34.990
really poking the bear and

00:17:35.000 --> 00:17:38.150
escalating this war on another level.

00:17:38.160 --> 00:17:40.270
I saw the Tomahawk missiles. The

00:17:40.280 --> 00:17:43.310
Pentagon cleared it today.

00:17:43.320 --> 00:17:45.630
They said, 'You

00:17:45.640 --> 00:17:47.750
can have them,'but Trump has to

00:17:47.760 --> 00:17:49.630
okay it. We don't want him to okay

00:17:49.640 --> 00:17:50.830
that;

00:17:50.840 --> 00:17:52.070
it

00:17:52.080 --> 00:17:53.870
would be very bad.

00:17:53.880 --> 00:17:55.710
I saw what happens whenever this

00:17:55.720 --> 00:17:57.270
takes place. That

00:17:57.270 --> 00:17:57.280
is

00:17:57.280 --> 00:17:59.510
another prayer assignment.

00:18:02.360 --> 00:18:06.190
I believe my gift is a watchman's eye, a

00:18:06.200 --> 00:18:08.230
prophetic lens. I've told everybody this

00:18:08.240 --> 00:18:09.430
a thousand times: I don't consider

00:18:09.440 --> 00:18:11.110
myself a prophet.

00:18:11.120 --> 00:18:15.470
I consider myself a watchman who

00:18:15.470 --> 00:18:15.480
sees

00:18:15.480 --> 00:18:17.950
what's coming so we can avert it or

00:18:17.960 --> 00:18:21.550
stop it altogether,

00:18:32.760 --> 00:18:36.310
or lessen the effects.

00:18:36.320 --> 00:18:39.070
And so we see the Pentagon saying that

00:18:39.080 --> 00:18:41.790
today. That right there is

00:18:41.800 --> 00:18:44.510
a

00:18:44.510 --> 00:18:44.520
sign

00:18:44.520 --> 00:18:46.950
for what I have seen coming next.

00:18:46.960 --> 00:18:48.909
I saw women and children running

00:18:48.919 --> 00:18:51.350
from Moscow. I saw the Kremlin being hit

00:18:51.360 --> 00:18:53.350
and struck; it looks like a castle

00:18:53.360 --> 00:18:56.270
there. They blew it up and struck all

00:18:56.280 --> 00:18:58.909
around it. I am telling you by the

00:18:58.919 --> 00:19:00.510
Spirit of God, we don't want this. We

00:19:00.520 --> 00:19:02.350
don't want escalation. I saw Poland

00:19:02.360 --> 00:19:05.710
getting involved. I saw

00:19:05.720 --> 00:19:08.110
Romania. I saw

00:19:08.120 --> 00:19:10.830
Belarus.

00:19:10.840 --> 00:19:13.350
So many other places were becoming

00:19:13.360 --> 00:19:14.710
involved, and there was snow on the

00:19:14.720 --> 00:19:17.149
ground. I saw people with snowsuits on, and

00:19:17.159 --> 00:19:19.590
they were in hand-to-hand combat like

00:19:19.600 --> 00:19:22.230
they are right now—trench warfare in

00:19:22.240 --> 00:19:24.110
Ukraine against Russia.

00:19:24.110 --> 00:19:24.120
When

00:19:24.120 --> 00:19:26.590
they said 7,000 men and women

00:19:26.600 --> 00:19:29.750
are dying a day in Ukraine and in

00:19:29.760 --> 00:19:31.149
Russia,

00:19:31.159 --> 00:19:33.030
that is ridiculous.

00:19:33.040 --> 00:19:34.750
7,000

00:19:34.760 --> 00:19:40.310
people a day die in Ukraine and Russia.

00:19:42.679 --> 00:19:45.110
I didn't realize it;

00:19:45.120 --> 00:19:46.149
we were talking about

00:19:46.149 --> 00:19:46.159
how

00:19:46.159 --> 00:19:47.830
that is terrible. Those are somebody's

00:19:47.840 --> 00:19:50.830
sons. Those are somebody's dads.

00:19:50.840 --> 00:19:55.270
So we pray for the

00:19:55.280 --> 00:19:57.950
escalation to

00:19:57.960 --> 00:19:59.670
come down. I know what

00:19:59.680 --> 00:20:01.670
the Lord has shown me about signs of

00:20:01.680 --> 00:20:03.230
the times and where we are in the last

00:20:03.240 --> 00:20:04.670
of the last days,

00:20:04.680 --> 00:20:06.750
that we will see wars and rumors of wars. We

00:20:06.750 --> 00:20:06.760
are

00:20:06.760 --> 00:20:08.830
going to see things,

00:20:08.840 --> 00:20:10.950
but I believe that we are still

00:20:10.960 --> 00:20:13.910
to pray

00:20:13.920 --> 00:20:15.950
regardless of the escalation of

00:20:15.960 --> 00:20:20.310
where we are. We are still to pray. Some

00:20:20.310 --> 00:20:20.320
might say,

00:20:20.320 --> 00:20:21.590
'Well, it's going to happen anyway.'No,

00:20:21.590 --> 00:20:21.600
I am

00:20:21.600 --> 00:20:25.070
still going to pray. I

00:20:25.070 --> 00:20:25.080
am

00:20:25.080 --> 00:20:26.430
going to pray for your kids if they

00:20:26.430 --> 00:20:26.440
are

00:20:26.440 --> 00:20:28.510
on the front line. I would pray;

00:20:28.520 --> 00:20:30.110
I hope you would pray for mine if they were.

00:20:31.520 --> 00:20:33.310
We have Christian brothers and sisters

00:20:33.320 --> 00:20:35.150
over there right now in Ukraine

00:20:35.150 --> 00:20:35.160
whose

00:20:35.160 --> 00:20:36.670
sons are over there

00:20:36.680 --> 00:20:38.270
fighting. They are thinking,

00:20:38.280 --> 00:20:40.070
'Is he going to be in a body bag on the

00:20:40.080 --> 00:20:41.150
way home?

00:20:41.160 --> 00:20:42.590
Is he going to be left

00:20:42.600 --> 00:20:44.270
on the field

00:20:44.280 --> 00:20:46.510
for the birds to eat

00:20:46.510 --> 00:20:46.520
him?'Those

00:20:46.520 --> 00:20:49.390
are somebody's kids.

00:20:50.800 --> 00:20:53.710
To not pray... it's just,

00:20:53.720 --> 00:20:55.710
'Whatever will be, will be,

00:20:55.710 --> 00:20:55.720
brother.'Well,

00:20:55.720 --> 00:20:57.150
you wouldn't act that way if

00:20:57.160 --> 00:21:00.550
that was your family.

00:21:00.560 --> 00:21:02.470
You still pray.

00:21:02.480 --> 00:21:04.190
You still pray for protection. You still

00:21:04.200 --> 00:21:06.670
intercede for the people, and God help

00:21:06.680 --> 00:21:07.630
them.

00:21:07.630 --> 00:21:07.640
That

00:21:07.640 --> 00:21:09.270
is

00:21:09.280 --> 00:21:10.950
what I do for yours; that

00:21:10.950 --> 00:21:10.960
is

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:13.350
what I pray you do for mine. There

00:21:13.350 --> 00:21:13.360
are

00:21:13.360 --> 00:21:15.510
Christians over there

00:21:15.520 --> 00:21:17.270
that love the Lord, probably

00:21:17.280 --> 00:21:18.670
more than we do.

00:21:18.680 --> 00:21:20.230
It

00:21:20.240 --> 00:21:22.150
is

00:21:22.160 --> 00:21:24.710
just sad to me.

00:21:24.720 --> 00:21:26.670
7,000. And we saw what happened to

00:21:26.680 --> 00:21:28.430
Jamaica. The Lord

00:21:28.440 --> 00:21:29.710
told me it would hit and all the things

00:21:29.720 --> 00:21:31.430
would happen; it

00:21:31.440 --> 00:21:33.350
really messed up that island.

00:21:33.360 --> 00:21:34.350
I don't know how

00:21:34.360 --> 00:21:36.350
many people have perished from that, but

00:21:36.350 --> 00:21:36.360
I

00:21:36.360 --> 00:21:38.510
believe with all my heart

00:21:38.520 --> 00:21:39.950
that what

00:21:39.960 --> 00:21:41.590
the devil meant for bad, God is going to

00:21:41.600 --> 00:21:43.430
get the good from it. We are going to turn

00:21:43.440 --> 00:21:45.790
it around. I believe that we are always

00:21:45.800 --> 00:21:47.350
on the victory side of things. We

00:21:47.350 --> 00:21:47.360
are

00:21:47.360 --> 00:21:49.630
not the victim; we

00:21:49.630 --> 00:21:49.640
are

00:21:49.640 --> 00:21:51.550
the victor, and we have

00:21:51.560 --> 00:21:53.350
authority. And that is what I wanted,

00:21:53.360 --> 00:21:56.230
Diana, before we start praying tonight. I

00:21:56.240 --> 00:21:59.310
want Diana to read this book by Sister

00:21:59.310 --> 00:21:59.320
Billye

00:21:59.320 --> 00:22:00.910
Brim, 'The Authority of

00:22:00.910 --> 00:22:00.920
the Believer and

00:22:00.920 --> 00:22:03.870
How to Use

00:22:03.870 --> 00:22:03.880
It.'This

00:22:03.880 --> 00:22:06.070
is the part on how

00:22:06.080 --> 00:22:07.710
to use it.

00:22:07.720 --> 00:22:09.030
So we are going to apply it. She

00:22:09.030 --> 00:22:09.040
will

00:22:09.040 --> 00:22:11.669
read it, and I want

00:22:11.679 --> 00:22:14.430
you to repeat the prayer part about your

00:22:14.440 --> 00:22:16.910
household, your family, your

00:22:16.920 --> 00:22:19.310
grandchildren, your children, your

00:22:19.320 --> 00:22:21.630
husband, or your wife, whatever it may be.

00:22:21.640 --> 00:22:23.350
You use it and pray over your

00:22:23.360 --> 00:22:24.950
family,

00:22:24.960 --> 00:22:26.870
but your mountain has to hear your

00:22:26.880 --> 00:22:29.830
voice. Brandon cannot cover it, and Diana

