You come here to Diana and me and we pray

02:04:03.800 --> 02:04:04.870
with you,

02:04:04.880 --> 02:04:06.990
and you trust us, and I don't

02:04:07.000 --> 02:04:10.190
take that lightly.

02:04:10.200 --> 02:04:13.150
We've been wounded greatly by a lot of

02:04:13.160 --> 02:04:15.590
good leaders, bad leaders,

02:04:15.600 --> 02:04:17.950
by people that were big leaders,

02:04:17.960 --> 02:04:22.470
and you walk away crushed.

02:04:22.480 --> 02:04:24.430
You just look at it and you go, 'Man,

02:04:24.440 --> 02:04:27.070
I know they're just human and we

02:04:27.080 --> 02:04:28.950
put them on a pedestal.'But there are so

02:04:28.960 --> 02:04:30.630
many of you

02:04:30.640 --> 02:04:32.470
that have left. I

02:04:32.470 --> 02:04:32.480
say,

02:04:32.480 --> 02:04:33.670
'Where do you go to church?'I come

02:04:33.680 --> 02:04:34.830
across people all the time. 'I don't go

02:04:34.840 --> 02:04:36.270
to church anymore. I refuse to go to

02:04:36.280 --> 02:04:38.310
church. I don't like church anymore. I

02:04:38.320 --> 02:04:41.070
watch you online,

02:04:41.070 --> 02:04:41.080
Brandon.'I'm

02:04:41.080 --> 02:04:43.830
like, 'Wow,

02:04:43.840 --> 02:04:48.630
what hurt

02:04:48.630 --> 02:04:48.640
you?'Pastors—I

02:04:48.640 --> 02:04:51.150
say, 'Yeah, I know

02:04:51.160 --> 02:04:52.990
they're human.

02:04:52.990 --> 02:04:53.000
They've

02:04:53.000 --> 02:04:58.310
got issues just like I've got

02:04:58.310 --> 02:04:58.320
issues.'But

02:04:58.320 --> 02:05:00.110
I just know that the Holy

02:05:00.110 --> 02:05:00.120
Spirit's

02:05:00.120 --> 02:05:03.230
wanting to restore some people tonight.

02:05:03.240 --> 02:05:05.190
There are so many times I wouldn't go to

02:05:05.200 --> 02:05:06.310
