02:05:06.320 --> 02:05:08.070
dollars to go to church.

02:05:08.080 --> 02:05:10.910
I was so angry at things.

02:05:10.920 --> 02:05:11.830
I said,

02:05:11.840 --> 02:05:13.990
'I don't care if they offered me a

02:05:14.000 --> 02:05:16.630
winning lottery

02:05:16.630 --> 02:05:16.640
ticket.'I'll

02:05:16.640 --> 02:05:18.110
be quite frank with you. I'll use

02:05:18.120 --> 02:05:19.150
the word. I said, 'They can all go to

02:05:19.160 --> 02:05:20.390
hell.'That's

02:05:20.400 --> 02:05:22.350
what I said.

02:05:22.360 --> 02:05:24.270
They can all go to hell. I don't want to

02:05:24.280 --> 02:05:27.350
do anything with them.

02:05:27.360 --> 02:05:29.310
And

02:05:29.320 --> 02:05:34.270
I was wounded so bad by so many people.

02:05:34.280 --> 02:05:37.110
And I realize that they're just

02:05:37.120 --> 02:05:40.550
people.

02:05:40.560 --> 02:05:43.270
But God wants to restore back

02:05:43.280 --> 02:05:46.030
what you have let hurt you so bad, and He

02:05:46.040 --> 02:05:48.870
wants a freshness. I want you to find

02:05:48.880 --> 02:05:51.190
Him again.

02:05:51.200 --> 02:05:53.070
I want you to have an authentic

02:05:53.080 --> 02:05:55.510
relationship with Him again

02:05:55.520 --> 02:05:58.270
where you're able to go and sit in a

02:05:58.280 --> 02:06:02.070
church service and get blessed by

02:06:02.070 --> 02:06:02.080
it—not

02:06:02.080 --> 02:06:04.350
about the money or about laying hands on

02:06:04.350 --> 02:06:04.360
the

02:06:04.360 --> 02:06:06.990
sick. Your relative might have died from

02:06:07.000 --> 02:06:08.750
