02:06:12.720 --> 02:06:14.510
you must have had sin in your life,

02:06:14.520 --> 02:06:16.350
brother, because that's what

02:06:16.350 --> 02:06:16.360
happened.'Or

02:06:16.360 --> 02:06:19.310
Charlie Kirk died because he didn't apply

02:06:19.320 --> 02:06:22.430
the blood.

02:06:22.440 --> 02:06:23.950
'Well, if he would have known his

02:06:23.960 --> 02:06:25.510
authority and he would have been walking

02:06:25.520 --> 02:06:28.230
in it, he wouldn't have

02:06:28.230 --> 02:06:28.240
died.'Those

02:06:28.240 --> 02:06:31.150
words hurt.

02:06:31.160 --> 02:06:33.510
And I've heard it before. I've been told

02:06:33.520 --> 02:06:35.630
that: 'Well, Charlie Kirk

02:06:35.640 --> 02:06:37.390
died because he didn't know his

02:06:37.400 --> 02:06:39.190
authority. Because if he would have known

02:06:39.200 --> 02:06:41.510
his authority and he would have done it,

02:06:41.520 --> 02:06:43.790
he wouldn't have

02:06:43.790 --> 02:06:43.800
died.'And

02:06:43.800 --> 02:06:44.990
you want to go, 'How do you know

02:06:45.000 --> 02:06:49.430
that?'I

02:06:49.440 --> 02:06:53.710
was told the same thing about Megan:

02:06:53.720 --> 02:06:54.910
'You must have had sin in your life,

02:06:54.920 --> 02:06:55.990
Brandon, because you've got a daughter with

02:06:56.000 --> 02:06:57.430
