02:06:57.440 --> 02:06:59.510
She's autistic because you have sin in

02:06:59.520 --> 02:07:01.590
your life. It must be

02:07:01.600 --> 02:07:03.790
a demon, and you need to cast those

02:07:03.800 --> 02:07:05.230
