02:07:15.600 --> 02:07:17.390
don't know if it's a devil; I'm just

02:07:17.400 --> 02:07:18.790
looking for somebody to help me because I'm

02:07:18.800 --> 02:07:20.670
in the middle of this pit and I can't

02:07:20.680 --> 02:07:24.070
get out. And I'm hurting bad.

02:07:24.080 --> 02:07:26.310
My marriage is suffering. I'm suffering.

02:07:26.320 --> 02:07:28.270
We're financially broke. We filed

02:07:28.280 --> 02:07:30.110
bankruptcy. We've got all this stuff

02:07:30.120 --> 02:07:32.150
going on and we're struggling.

02:07:32.160 --> 02:07:34.030
We can't get out of this hole. But

02:07:34.030 --> 02:07:34.040
we've

02:07:34.040 --> 02:07:35.670
got some preacher telling us it's

02:07:35.680 --> 02:07:37.190
because we've got sin in

02:07:37.190 --> 02:07:37.200
our

02:07:37.200 --> 02:07:38.390
lives.

02:07:38.400 --> 02:07:41.110
But I'm going to tell you this:

02:07:42.120 --> 02:07:44.070
sometimes we live in a fallen world and

02:07:44.080 --> 02:07:47.590
bad things happen to good people.

02:07:47.600 --> 02:07:49.350
I don't know why.

02:07:49.350 --> 02:07:49.360
It

02:07:49.360 --> 02:07:50.750
just happens.

02:07:50.760 --> 02:07:52.310
But it's not because you sometimes don't

02:07:52.320 --> 02:07:54.190
use your authority, because I've seen some

02:07:54.200 --> 02:07:55.750
people use their authority that were

02:07:55.760 --> 02:07:58.350
real

02:07:58.350 --> 02:07:58.360
jerks—spiritually

02:07:58.360 --> 02:08:01.630
big-headed, like

02:08:01.630 --> 02:08:01.640
celebrities—and

02:08:01.640 --> 02:08:03.390
you go, 'Oh, come on. Get off of your

02:08:03.400 --> 02:08:05.950
high horse.'The more I get in this and

02:08:05.960 --> 02:08:08.870
the bigger my platform gets, I see it

02:08:08.880 --> 02:08:10.790
and I refuse to. But I understand

02:08:10.800 --> 02:08:13.709
sometimes that people try to put people

02:08:13.719 --> 02:08:15.950
like you—you're the answer to

02:08:15.960 --> 02:08:18.470
their problems. And it's like one

02:08:18.480 --> 02:08:20.670
young man said, 'I'm not letting go until

02:08:20.680 --> 02:08:22.150
you bless me, Brandon. I'm going to talk

02:08:22.160 --> 02:08:24.150
to you until you bless me.

02:08:24.160 --> 02:08:26.150
There's an anointing on you, and I want

02:08:26.160 --> 02:08:27.709
you to help me with my crypto. I want

02:08:27.719 --> 02:08:28.830
you to help me do this. I want you to do

02:08:28.840 --> 02:08:30.390
that. And I'm not going to let you go

02:08:30.400 --> 02:08:32.270
until you bless me.'And I go, 'But I'm

02:08:32.280 --> 02:08:36.590
not the source. Jesus

02:08:36.590 --> 02:08:36.600
is

02:08:36.600 --> 02:08:38.470
