02:08:42.200 --> 02:08:43.790
anything. I can't even give you a word.

02:08:46.320 --> 02:08:48.470
The only thing is, I'm completely

02:08:48.480 --> 02:08:50.110
yielded to the Holy Ghost on this

02:08:50.120 --> 02:08:52.150
channel.

02:08:52.160 --> 02:08:54.190
Anything else is just Brandon and it is

02:08:54.200 --> 02:08:56.790
stinky.

02:08:56.800 --> 02:08:59.830
I can't do anything without

02:08:59.830 --> 02:08:59.840
Him.'And

02:08:59.840 --> 02:09:02.270
that's why I want you to know:

02:09:02.280 --> 02:09:04.310
God wants to restore back the joy

02:09:04.320 --> 02:09:06.190
that you've lost because of it. That's what

02:09:06.200 --> 02:09:07.470
He said to me when I was praying right

02:09:07.480 --> 02:09:08.350
then.

02:09:08.360 --> 02:09:09.870
He said, 'I want to restore back that

02:09:09.880 --> 02:09:11.190
hurt that people have in their

02:09:11.200 --> 02:09:16.510
heart because of charismatic flakiness

02:09:16.520 --> 02:09:18.830
where you're just

02:09:18.830 --> 02:09:18.840
wounded.'And

02:09:18.840 --> 02:09:20.710
God wants to bring joy in

02:09:20.720 --> 02:09:22.590
your marriage again, joy back in

02:09:22.600 --> 02:09:24.710
your hearts again where you can go back

02:09:24.720 --> 02:09:27.430
and enjoy church

02:09:27.430 --> 02:09:27.440
and

02:09:27.440 --> 02:09:30.110
enjoy just having fellowship.

02:09:30.120 --> 02:09:31.350
And if you don't want to, that's great.

02:09:31.360 --> 02:09:32.870
It might take a work in progress just

02:09:32.880 --> 02:09:34.430
