02:09:47.120 --> 02:09:50.230
the camera. All

02:09:50.230 --> 02:09:50.240
I

02:09:50.240 --> 02:09:52.750
know

02:09:52.750 --> 02:09:52.760
is

02:09:52.760 --> 02:09:54.670
I cried a lot of

02:09:54.680 --> 02:09:55.830
tears

02:09:55.840 --> 02:09:57.230
and I had a lot of sleepless

02:09:57.240 --> 02:10:00.190
