I'd like to give church another try.

02:11:05.430 --> 02:11:05.440
I'd

02:11:05.440 --> 02:11:07.550
like to give Jesus another try.'I was

02:11:07.560 --> 02:11:09.510
wounded by the prosperity gospel. I was

02:11:09.520 --> 02:11:12.830
ruined. I was wounded by

02:11:12.840 --> 02:11:14.870
the healing... I was wounded by all these

02:11:14.880 --> 02:11:17.390
