02:11:19.800 --> 02:11:21.630
or whatever. I don't know. Whoever it

02:11:21.640 --> 02:11:23.630
was that hurt

02:11:23.630 --> 02:11:23.640
you—your

02:11:23.640 --> 02:11:26.030
pastor, whatever.

02:11:26.040 --> 02:11:28.230
But tonight,

02:11:28.240 --> 02:11:29.990
I want you to get special prayer. I want

02:11:30.000 --> 02:11:32.030
