02:11:36.160 --> 02:11:38.950
will become real to you.

02:11:38.960 --> 02:11:40.550
Say, "Father, I'm coming home.

02:11:40.560 --> 02:11:42.590
I'm not going to let anybody else keep

02:11:42.600 --> 02:11:44.070
me from you.

02:11:44.080 --> 02:11:46.870
I'm running to you

02:11:46.880 --> 02:11:48.470
like

02:11:48.480 --> 02:11:50.950
the prodigal son, the prodigal

02:11:50.960 --> 02:11:53.270
daughter.

02:11:53.280 --> 02:11:56.230
Tonight, I want a clean

02:11:56.230 --> 02:11:56.240
start."If

02:11:56.240 --> 02:11:57.830
this is ministering to you and you

02:11:57.840 --> 02:11:59.430
feel that stirring

02:11:59.430 --> 02:11:59.440
on

02:11:59.440 --> 02:12:00.990
the inside of you, I want you to

02:12:01.000 --> 02:12:02.830
