02:12:02.840 --> 02:12:03.910
"Brandon, this is ministering to

02:12:03.920 --> 02:12:05.910
me. I need you to pray for me.

02:12:05.920 --> 02:12:08.030
I want to come home

02:12:08.030 --> 02:12:08.040
today."I

02:12:08.040 --> 02:12:09.870
was wounded by

02:12:09.880 --> 02:12:12.670
preachers. I was wounded by evangelists.

02:12:12.680 --> 02:12:14.550
I was wounded by this. But

02:12:14.560 --> 02:12:16.110
tonight I want to give God a fresh

02:12:16.120 --> 02:12:18.950
start. I want you to

02:12:18.960 --> 02:12:21.830
