02:12:23.440 --> 02:12:24.990
people.

02:12:25.000 --> 02:12:27.990
I ask you to help me.

02:12:28.000 --> 02:12:30.750
I want to release this bitterness and

02:12:30.750 --> 02:12:30.760
the

02:12:30.760 --> 02:12:32.950
anger that I have

02:12:32.960 --> 02:12:37.070
towards people.

02:12:37.080 --> 02:12:38.470
There's no one that's ever going to help

02:12:38.480 --> 02:12:41.606
you other than Jesus Christ.

02:12:41.720 --> 02:12:43.350
But I'm trying to tell you this:

02:12:43.360 --> 02:12:46.710
