02:13:21.360 --> 02:13:23.750
selling on eBay,

02:13:23.760 --> 02:13:27.910
selling on Poshmark."I enjoy it

02:13:27.910 --> 02:13:27.920
and

02:13:27.920 --> 02:13:30.077
we love it;

02:13:30.280 --> 02:13:33.430
